<%= link_to 'OverWine.io', root_path, id: 'brand' %>

<section id="jumbotron">
  <div id="jumbotron-content-wrapper">
    <div>
      <h1>Relax. Let us build your next MVP.</h1>
      <p>With over 10 years of industry experience working with startups and small businesses alike, we can help get your idea off the ground and take it to the next level.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= link_to image_tag("arrow-down.svg"), '#', id: 'scroll-down' %>
  <%= video_tag ["/videos/675073365.mp4", "/videos/675073365.webm"], poster: image_path('675073365.jpg'), autoplay: true, loop: true, muted: true %>
</section>

<section id="who-we-are">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      We're a pair of full-stack engineers specializing in Ruby on Rails located in the San Francisco Bay Area. Although
      we both have full-time jobs in Silicon Valley, we also enjoy a little freelancing on the side which gives us a
      chance to explore new ideas and work across different industries.
    </p>
    <div class="profile-card">
      <figure class="jeff"></figure>
      <article>
        <h3>Jeff Miller</h3>
        <p>
          Jeff is a Senior Software Engineer at <%= link_to 'Cognoa', 'https://www.cognoa.com', target: '_blank' %>, whose
          mission is to employ big data and machine learning to vastly improve early childhood detection of developmental
          disabilities including autism.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><%= link_to icon('home'), 'http://humani.se', target: '_blank' %></li>
          <li><%= link_to icon('github'), 'https://www.github.com/ibanez270dx', target: '_blank' %></li>
          <li><%= link_to icon('linkedin'), 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ibanez270dx', target: '_blank' %></li>
          <li><%= link_to icon('envelope'), 'mailto:jeff@humani.se', target: '_blank' %></li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="profile-card">
      <figure class="gianna"></figure>
      <article>
        <h3>Gianna Fusaro</h3>
        <p>
          Gianna is a Software Engineer at <%= link_to 'Wurl', 'http://www.wurl.com', target: '_blank' %>, where she
          designs and develops tools to help bridge the gap between traditional cable TV and modern internet-enabled streaming services.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><%= link_to icon('home'), 'http://www.gianna.codes', target: '_blank' %></li>
          <li><%= link_to icon('github'), 'https://www.github.com/giannafusaro', target: '_blank' %></li>
          <li><%= link_to icon('linkedin'), 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/giannafusaro', target: '_blank' %></li>
          <li><%= link_to icon('envelope'), 'mailto:gianna@gianna.codes', target: '_blank' %></li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="what-we-do">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>
      Our process is simple -- we take care of the full-cycle of web application development from initial concept to deployment.
      This includes requirements elicitation, designing, coding, testing and devops services.
    </p>

    <ul id="services">
      <li>
        <%= image_tag('gifs/animat-pencil-color.gif') %>
        <h4>1. Gather Requirements</h4>
        <p>We work with you to distill your vision into a crystal-clear set of requirements and deliverables so we can build you the best possible product.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <%= image_tag('gifs/animat-responsive-color.gif') %>
        <h4>2. Prototype and Design</h4>
        <p>We ensure your MVP provides an intuitive and memorable experience while functioning seamlessly across all devices and platforms.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <%= image_tag('gifs/animat-diamond-color.gif') %>
        <h4>3. Code, Code, Code</h4>
        <p>Using industry-leading best practices, we build a rock-solid MVP that you can test with your target audience or even pitch directly to investors.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <%= image_tag('gifs/animat-rocket-color.gif') %>
        <h4>4. Launch!</h4>
        <p>Gain valuable insights while attracting investors, cofounders, and early employees with a working MVP deployed on scalable cloud-based hosting.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <% if false %>
      <ul id="tools">
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-photoshop-cutout'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-illustrator-cutout'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-ruby'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-rails'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-html5'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-css3'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-coffeescript'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-github'), '#' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to content_tag(:i, nil, class: 'hu-javascript-cutout'), '#' %></li>
      </ul>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>

<section id='our-projects'>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Featured Projects</h2>

    <div class="project">
      <figure>
        <%= link_to image_tag('projects/superpups.png'), 'http://www.superpups.biz', target: '_blank' %>
      </figure>
      <div class="flex-wrapper">
        <article>
          <h3>SuperPups</h3>
          <p>
            Small business website for San Mateo based pet salon, SuperPups. Includes a custom photo gallery and
            custom content management system.
          </p>
          <%= link_to 'www.superpups.biz', 'http://www.superpups.biz', target: '_blank' %>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <figure>
        <%= link_to image_tag('projects/myprohero.png'), 'http://www.myprohero.com', target: '_blank' %>
      </figure>
      <div class="flex-wrapper">
        <article>
          <h3>MyProHero</h3>
          <div>
            Formerly iSportsDevelopment
          </div>
          <p>
            Web app for facilitating and recording live online sports coaching sessions through Google Hangouts and YouTube.
          </p>
          <%= link_to 'www.myprohero.com', 'https://www.myprohero.com/', target: '_blank' %>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact-us">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Let's Talk</h1>
    <p>
      Get a free quote for web application design and development<br />
      <small>Don't worry, we hate spam too. We won't share your email with anyone.</small>
    </p>
    <%= form_tag contact_path, remote: true do %>
      <%= email_field_tag :email, nil, placeholder: 'Your email address' %>
      <%= text_area_tag :message, nil, placeholder: 'A brief description of your project', rows: 8 %>
      <%= submit_tag 'Send' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>
